name: The Gym Elkins Park
overview: The Gym does not provide a cookie-cutter, one size fits all fitness solution. Every Member is unique with his/her personal fitness objectives. Depending on how fast you want to achieve your health, weight management, and fitness objectives; and the amount of personal motivation and supervision you require, The Gym is the only fitness center in the area that offers you three Unstoppable Fitness Solutions–Personal Training, Bootcamp, and Fitness Membership. One of our three fitness solutions is just perfect for you!
